com.b2international.snowowl.snomed.mrcm

Interface RelationshipConceptSetDefinition

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.cdo.CDOObject, org.eclipse.emf.cdo.common.id.CDOWithID, ConceptModelComponent, ConceptSetDefinition, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    RelationshipConceptSetDefinitionImpl

    public interface RelationshipConceptSetDefinition
extends ConceptSetDefinition
    A representation of the model object 'Relationship Concept Set Definition'. Concept set definition describing concepts which include a relationship of the given type and destination.

    The following features are supported:

    • Type Concept Id
    • Destination Concept Id

    See Also:
    MrcmPackage.getRelationshipConceptSetDefinition()
